<dl id="n42013g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42013g">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42013g"> 13(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> temerity</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">They all agree in declaring that it is a most difficult and dangerous art; they all confess that the least error of judgement, the least imprudence or temerity, when storming the impregnable citadel, is certain death (spiritual, of course) to the confessor and the penitent. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 45</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
